{"text_id":110833,"tokens":["I"," believe"," that"," the"," school"," policy"," of"," requiring"," a"," certain"," grade"," point"," average"," (","GPA",")"," for"," participation"," in"," sports"," and"," other"," activities"," is"," misguided"," and"," has"," a"," negative"," impact"," on"," students","'"," academic"," performance"," and"," overall"," health",".","\n\n","On"," one"," hand",","," the"," expectation"," that"," students"," must"," maintain"," a"," certain"," GPA"," to"," participate"," in"," extracurricular"," activities"," creates"," an"," unnecessary"," level"," of"," stress"," and"," anxiety","."," Research"," has"," shown"," that"," high"," levels"," of"," stress"," can"," negatively"," impact"," cognitive"," function",","," memory",","," and"," overall"," well","-","being","."," Additionally",","," the"," pressure"," to"," maintain"," a"," certain"," GPA"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," focus"," solely"," on"," grades",","," rather"," than"," a"," holistic"," education"," that"," incorporates"," personal"," development"," and"," well","-","being",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," the"," emphasis"," on"," GPA"," can"," stifle"," creativity",","," critical"," thinking",","," and"," problem","-","solving"," skills",","," as"," students"," become"," overly"," focused"," on"," grades"," rather"," than"," exploring"," their"," interests"," and"," talents","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," narrow","-","minded"," approach"," to"," education",","," leading"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," motivation"," and"," engagement"," in"," academic"," pursuits",".","\n\n","On"," the"," other"," hand",","," requiring"," a"," certain"," GPA"," for"," participation"," in"," sports"," and"," other"," activities"," can"," actually"," improve"," academic"," performance","."," By"," linking"," extracurricular"," participation"," to"," academic"," performance",","," students"," are"," incentiv","ized"," to"," stay"," on"," top"," of"," their"," school","work"," and"," maintain"," good"," grades","."," Additionally",","," sports"," and"," extracurricular"," activities"," have"," been"," shown"," to"," improve"," mental"," and"," physical"," health",","," including"," reducing"," stress"," and"," anxiety",","," improving"," self","-","esteem",","," and"," providing"," a"," sense"," of"," community"," and"," belonging",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," the"," GPA"," requirement"," may"," have"," some"," benefits",","," I"," strongly"," believe"," that"," it"," is"," a"," misguided"," policy"," that"," has"," negative"," consequences"," for"," students","'"," academic"," performance"," and"," overall"," health","."," I"," suggest"," that"," schools"," consider"," a"," more"," balanced"," approach",","," incorporating"," both"," extracurricular"," activities"," and"," academic"," support"," services"," to"," promote"," a"," well","-","rounded"," education","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}